requirement:
Yêu Cầu Công Việc


              -	Hands-on practice in at least one web application framework (Laravel or Symfony or Ruby on Rails or Django);

              -	Experience in ORM, HTML5/CSS3, JavaScript OOP and jQuery, OOP, DI/IoC, SOLID principles and software development best practices;

              -	Proficient in code review, code refactoring, Unit Testing;

              -	Experience in one open source CMS systems (Wordpress, Drupal);

              -	Ability to work independently with high self-motivation and self-management and good team player;

              -	Good in communication, especially in English;

              -	Prefer for additional skills:

              o	Experience with AngularJS or similar Javascript MVC framework;

              o	Good knowledge in Clould - specifically AWS, NoSQL databases, NodeJS/Golang, TDD/BDD;

              o	Build scripts with Phing/Capistrano/Fabric;

              o	Familiar with the integration APIs and tools.


